snippet.title: 3 GUESTS KICKED OFF THE PODCAST! Do Women OVER-S*xualize Themselves From Marriage? (HEATED DEBATE)
snippet.description:
➜ 🕔Time Stamps🕔
0:00-1:02 Intro, Announcements, Social Media/content plugs (like the video on your way in family.)
6:27 Future episode on addressing The myth that is "grape culture"
7:25 Ladies Introduce themselves
8:57 Superchats
16:56 Why did your last relationship end, and whose fault was it?
18:54 Blame it on the...alcohol? babygirl.
21:17 First question continued.
30:48 What loyalty means for men and what it means for women.
31:27 Wake up Castle!!! (Like the video family.)
32:51 First question continued
35:08 Superchats
40:18 What do you want when it comes to dating?
46:11 Femcap?
47:28 Second question continued
53:07...here we go.
53:36 Women sexualize themselves, here's how and why. Analogy time.
58:12 Teachable moment, (Pay attention y'all)
59:19 Ask the chat, would you wife a woman who sexualizes herself?
1:01:19 Teachable moment continued(like the video y'all)
1:12:11 let's take it to the extreme sheesh!
1:12:55 Would you close your social medias for the man you want to marry?
1:15:02 Men and women do not play by the same rules in life. Ie. Posting pics (Teachable Moment)
1:17:25 Peep the interaction between Myron and the women. Comment what you notice.
1:18:57 One of the ladies disrespects Myron, he checks her.
1:20:30 Superchats!
1:21:03 Men and women play by a different set of rules (short analogy)
1:23:47 One of the ladies shares their opinion on the value that women bring.
1:26:40 Peep the misandry
1:28:40 Goal post officially switched...
1:29:12 Women, other men should be invisible to you when you're in a relationship or married. Take notes.
1:29:28 Chris...the goat, chimes in.
1:35:35...Myron teaching women to construct a proper argument? Guys, like the damn video!
1:27:50 In society, women's preferences are praised, men's preferences are demonized...
1:39:16 One of the ladies, seems to get it.
1:40:22 IG video reaction.
1:42:07 Ladies Reaction to the IG video.
1:44:23 Men do not cheat, they excercise options. (Shout-out to Kevin Samuels)
1:47:20 Myron asks If you're in a relationship, can you have sex with other men?
1:52:35 If you had your ideal man, is giving up sexualizing yourself really an issue?
1:54:37 What is a "Conscious relationship"??? (Like the video y'all)
1:57:04 A "Conscious Relationship" is a social construct, here's why.
2:02:17 Women are not built to support men long term, here's why.
2:03:27 What makes women, attractive to men?
2:06:12 Women listening to respond, not to understand. (pay attention y'all)
2:06:56 Chris! Come on bro! (Comedic moment)
2:14:12 Studies show, the more women have become liberated the more unhappy they have become.
2:15:09 Clearly, she does not get what Myron is conveying.
2:17:44 This country was built on the traditional, nuclear family.
2:18:00 Growing issues with modern men.
2:19:12 Invest in pet food y'all. Also (like the video)
2:21:00 A woman's value is determined by what caliber of man you lock down.
2:23:15 Society has lied to women.
2:25:53 Hamster wheeling...
2:26:14 Someone gets Myron's point!
2:27:52 Superchats!
2:30:22 Myron goes back into how one of the ladies sexualizes herself on IG.
2:31:26 Superchats Continued
2:42:50 If a car is already bought, there should not be a for sale sign on it.
2:43:20 Opinion and fact are two different things (Teachable Moment)
2:46:47 (Proof) two of the ladies have not been listening for quite a while.
2:50:35 I FEEL attacked!
2:51:00 Superchats continued.
2:52:13 At what age would let your daughter post these type of pics (crazy answer)
2:52:42 Pulling up, one of the ladies IGs (for example)
2:53:17 Would you marry a female posting provocative pictures on IG?
2:56:54 Chris too funny y'all! (Like the video)
2:59:34 Men and women can not be plutonic friends.
3:00:00 (NOPE! Shout out to Coach Greg Adams) Myron goes in on the FACT that Fresh and Fit are (not Misogynistic)
3:07:07 One of the ladies chimes in, on the fact that Fresh and Fit are not Misogynistic.
3:08:08 WOO SAH ladies.
3:09:12 (Teachable moment) On physical contact between men and women.
3:11:38 Another one bites the dust. (Frank Castle)
3:12:22 Superchats
3:15:34 Remaining ladies plug their social medias
3:19:58 Outro
